name: The Wonder Tree -  canvas
description:
THE WONDER TREE
Larry Carlson

16 x 20" canvas
1 1/4" side profile

- Archival pigment print to matte canvas resulting in super color saturation and pop!

- The image wraps around the sides of the canvas allowing it to be hung beautifully with no frame.

- Canvas is glazed over the top with an acrylic varnish which protects it from sunlight and scratching.

- Certified archival.

- Signed by Larry Carlson on the back of the canvas.
